OL,7,FA young Co Down woman living with
OL,8,Fseveral disabilities has spoken to UTV
OL,9,Fabout her frustration at being on the
OL,10,Fhousing waiting list.
OL,12,FKelly Gill, who currently lives in a
OL,13,Fnursing home, has received a number of
OL,14,Foffers but feels that none of them
OL,15,Fhave been appropriate.
OL,17,FThe Housing Executive has said that
OL,18,Fevery effort has been made to help
OL,19,FKelly, and that she remains a priority.
