OL,7,FKelly lives with a severe neurological
OL,8,Fcondition which has led to her
OL,9,Fbecoming deaf and visually impaired.
OL,11,FShe has spent recent years in nursing
OL,12,Fhomes but wants to live independently.
OL,14,F"The nursing home that I am in is
OL,15,Flovely. The staff make it nice but
OL,16,Fultimately it is not home and never
OL,17,Fwill feel like my home.
OL,19,F"I am just feeling a bit lost because
OL,20,FI am a youngish woman. I do want to
OL,21,Flive my life and move on.
