OL,7,F"I just feel like I am stuck and being
OL,8,Fin the nursing home has a detrimental
OL,9,Feffect on my mental health", she said.
OL,11,FKelly is currently on the Housing
OL,12,FExecutive waiting list. She has had
OL,13,Foffers - including a property that was
OL,14,Fspecially adapted - but she suggested
OL,15,Fthat more work was needed.
OL,17,F"The front door my chair couldn't fit
OL,18,Fthrough properly without the arms
OL,19,Fbeing damaged.
