OL,7,F"In the end, they said they would not
OL,8,Fmake the adaptations until I accepted
OL,9,Fthe tenancy and lived in the house",
OL,10,Fshe told UTV.
OL,12,FKelly viewed two other houses though
OL,13,Fshe told us neither met her needs.
OL,15,FKelly recognises that there is
OL,16,Fpressure across the housing sector.
