OL,3,CYoung Co Down woman with disabilities
OL,4,C'frustrated' with wait for suitable
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"I know the situation is dire
OL,8,Fthroughout Northern Ireland and the
OL,9,FHousing Executive are limited but
OL,10,Fequally I feel like it is not just me
OL,11,Fin this situation.
OL,13,F"When I have addressed it with my
OL,14,Fhousing officer they have said that
OL,15,Fpeople have waited years", she added.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Housing Executive
OL,18,Fsaid: "We are very sympathetic to
OL,19,FKelly and we continue to treat this
OL,20,Fcase as a priority.
